Package com.groq.sdk.models.files

Class FileUploadRequest

java.lang.Object
com.groq.sdk.models.files.FileUploadRequest
public class FileUploadRequest extends Object
Represents a request to upload a file to the Groq API. Contains the file content, purpose, and filename for upload operations.
